headline.print_headline: Expert: No Accident With Gun in Porch Shooting
headline.main: Expert: No Accident With Gun in Porch Shooting

lead_paragraph: An expert says the shotgun used to kill a young woman on a porch in suburban Detroit wasn't accidentally fired by the homeowner.
